snippet.title: Dark Cloud: Trailer
snippet.description:
Part RPG, part town-building-simulator, this game does a little bit of everything and does it really stinkin' well. I'm excited to show you guys a major part of my childhood, and one of my all-time favorite PS2 games. Let's play Dark Cloud.

Begin Part 1: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a4ZX1RC8kbI&list=PLk4vyGhhIn_z0baJ8_-27idWXav805jXk&index=2

================================================
If you like what you see, go ahead and follow mah facebook/twitter. I update regularly! 
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/pages/Archtal...
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ArchTalko

Want to ask me a question directly and/or anonymously? Check out my blog on Tumblr!
